Citgo Petroleum Corp, a subsidiary ofSouthland Corp, said it raised the contract price it will payfor all grades of crude oil by 50 cts a barrel, effective Oct16    The increase brings Citgo's postings for the West TexasIntermediate and West Texas Sour grades to 19.00 dlrs/barrel,while Light Louisiana SWeet is now priced at 19.35 dlrs.    Citgo last changed it crude oil postings on Sept 9. Reuter&#3;